org.ow2.proactive.resourcemanager.authentication

Class RMFileLoginModule

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ow2.proactive.authentication.FileLoginModule
      • org.ow2.proactive.resourcemanager.authentication.RMFileLoginModule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LoginModule, Loggable

    public class RMFileLoginModule
extends FileLoginModule
    File login module implementation for resource manager. Extracts "login" and "group" files names from resource manager configuration and uses them to authenticate users.
